(7, '', '', 1, '', '原理： 使用 msmtp+mutt+shell来实现 之前在Linux下使用mail命令来发送邮件，配置起来比较麻烦，需要配置sendmail的很多东西。而且还必须启动sendmail才能保证邮件发送成功。其实我们就只要能发送邮件就可以，服务器多开个东西就等于多一个入侵的门。而且sendmail漏斗是很多的。那么有没有类似于foxmail,outlook这样的邮件客户端软件，并且有命令行的形式，来发送邮件呢。mutt和msmtp提供了一个', '原理：<br />\r\n<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 使用 msmtp+mutt+shell来实现</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \r\n之前在Linux下使用mail命令来发送邮件，配置起来比较麻烦，需要配置sendmail的很多东西。而且还必须启动sendmail才能保证邮件发\r\n送成功。其实我们就只要能发送邮件就可以，服务器多开个东西就等于多一个入侵的门。而且sendmail漏斗是很多的。那么有没有类似于\r\nfoxmail,outlook这样的邮件客户端软件，并且有命令行的形式，来发送邮件呢。mutt和msmtp提供了一个很好的解决方案。<br />\r\n开始：<br />\r\n<span>这里因为很多路径我写死了，所以最好按照我的安装路径来安装。或者根据自己的环境修改路径。注意后面的注释。</span><br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span>因为这个我已经写成sh文件，只要修改你的邮箱地址和密码再执行installMuttMsmtp.sh就可以。</span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href="/Uploads/file/20131004/20131004161915_67225.gz" target="_blank">install.sh</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	下面是install.sh的内容：\r\n</p>\r\n<b><span>我使用的是126的免费邮。如果你用别的，修改相应的smtp地址。后面的注释不用复制。</span><br />\r\n<span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#0070C0;">注意linux的注释是以“#”</span></span><br />\r\n<span>&nbsp;</span></b><br />\r\nmkdir -p /usr/local/msmtp/etc<br />\r\nvi&nbsp; /root/.msmtprc&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; #注意文件名前面有个“点"<br />\r\n<span>host smtp.126.com&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; #smtp地址<br />\r\ntls off<br />\r\nauth plain<br />\r\nfrom apacal@126.com&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; #从哪个邮件发出来<br />\r\nuser </span><span><span>apacal</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; #用户名<br />\r\npassword ***************</span><i> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span>#邮箱密码</span><br />\r\n</i><br />\r\nvi&nbsp; /root/.muttrc<br />\r\n<span>set sendmail="/usr/local/msmtp/bin/msmtp"&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; #</span><span>msmtp的安装位置。根据自己的情况改</span><br />\r\n<span>set use_from=yes<br />\r\nset from=</span><span><span>apacal@126.com</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>#用户名</span><br />\r\n<span>set envelope_from=yes</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nvi  /usr/local/msmtp/etc/msmtprc<br />\r\n<span>defaults <br />\r\naccount apacal &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; #用户名<br />\r\nhost smtp.126.com&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; # smtp -IP<br />\r\nfrom </span><span><span>apacal@126.com</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; #用户名 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\nauth login<br />\r\nport 25<br />\r\ntls off<br />\r\nuser&nbsp;</span><span>apacal@126.com</span><span style="color:#0000FF;">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp; #用户名 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><br />\r\n<span>password&nbsp;</span><span> *<span style="color:#0070C0;">*</span></span><span style="color:#0070C0;">****</span><span style="color:#0070C0;"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; #密码<br />\r\n<span>account default : apacal<br />\r\nlogfile /usr/local/msmtp/log/msmtp.log&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span>#用户名 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n以上3个文件就这样保存，请确保用户名、密码、stmp的正确性。再来：<br />\r\nmkdir -p /usr/local/msmtp/log<br />\r\necho ''set sendmail="/usr/local/msmtp/bin/msmtp"'' &gt;&gt;/etc/Muttrc<br />\r\necho "set use_from=yes" &gt;&gt;/etc/Muttrc<br />\r\necho ''set realname="<span><span style="color:#000000;">apacal@126.com</span></span>"'' &gt;&gt;/etc/Muttrc&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <b><span>#这里改成自己的邮箱</span></b><br />\r\necho ''set editor="vim"'' &gt;&gt;/etc/Muttrc<br />\r\n安装软件包msmtp<br />\r\ntar jxvf msmtp-1.4.21.tar.bz2<br />\r\ncd msmtp-1.4.21<br />\r\n./configure --prefix=/usr/local/msmtp<br />\r\nmake<br />\r\nsleep 3 <br />\r\nmake install<br />\r\nsleep 3<br />\r\ncd ..<br />\r\ntar zxvf mutt-1.5.21.tar.gz <br />\r\ncd mutt-1.5.21<br />\r\n./configure --prefix=/usr/local/mutt<br />\r\nmake<br />\r\nsleep 3<br />\r\nmake install<br />\r\nsleep 3<br />\r\ncd ..<br />\r\nln -s /usr/local/msmtp/bin/msmtp /usr/bin<br />\r\n这样就完成了<br />\r\n发送命令：<br />\r\n/usr/local/mutt/bin/mutt -s "邮件标题" 1612577280@qq.com&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这是测试邮件 -a /tmp/附件.txt<br />\r\n<span>&nbsp;</span>-s 邮件标题&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 紧接的是接收邮件地址&nbsp; -c 抄送地址&nbsp; "这是测试邮件"为邮件正文&nbsp;&nbsp; -a是附件<br />\r\n<br />\r\n收到邮件了<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<span>在./comfigure&nbsp; mutt时出现以下错误</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span></span>checking for initscr in -lunknown... no<br />\r\nconfigure: error: no curses library found&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	表示没有安转curses包，安装命令# apt-get libncurses5-devi<span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:Verdana, Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:19px;background-color:#28557E;"><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> <span></span></span>在编译mutt中，如果提示：checking whether this iconv is good enough... noconfigure: error: Try using libiconv instead\r\n</p>\r\n解决方法：<br />\r\n找到你的<span>libiconv</span>.<span>so</span>.2 一般都在/usr/的某个目录下<br />\r\n[root@sh49194 mutt-1.5.21]# find /usr/ -name  "libiconv.so*"<br />\r\n/usr/local/lib/libiconv.so.2.5.1<br />\r\n/usr/local/lib/libiconv.so.2<br />\r\n/usr/local/lib/libiconv.so<br />\r\n然后<br />\r\necho "/usr/local/lib/" &gt;&gt;/etc/ld.<span>so</span>.conf<br />\r\n执行<br />\r\nldconfig再次编译看看<br />\r\n还不行的话，直接做软链：<br />\r\n<span>ln</span> -s /usr/local/lib/libiconv.so.2 /usr/lib/<span>libiconv</span>.<span>so</span>.<span>2<br />\r\n<span>但是我的遇到： configure: error: no curses library found<br />\r\n安装：</span></span><span><span><span><span>ncurses就可以了<br />\r\n<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span>#yum -y install ncurses-devel<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n建立以mysqlbackup.sh文件，使用# crontab -e &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 自动执行<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span><br />\r\n</span><br />\r\n<span><span><span>mysqlbackup.sh&nbsp; <br />\r\n<span></span></span></span></span><br />\r\n<span><span><span><span style="color:#0070C0;">backupdir=/home/mysqlbakup<br />\r\ntime=` date +%Y%m%d `<br />\r\n/etc/init.d/mysqld stop<br />\r\ntar zcvf /home/mysqlbackup/mysql$time.tar.gz /var/lib/mysql<br />\r\n/etc/init.d/mysqld start<br />\r\n#删除7天前的备份<br />\r\nfind $backupdir -name "mysql*.tar.gz" -type f -mtime +7 -exec rm {} \\; &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1<br />\r\ncontent="<br />\r\n各位：<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 这是今天数据库的备份压缩包，注意查收。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此邮件自动发送，请勿回复。<br />\r\napacal<br />\r\n$time<br />\r\n"<br />\r\necho "$content" | /usr/local/mutt/bin/mutt -s "空气质量收集系<br />\r\n统数据库备份" 1612577280@qq.com 316259181@qq.com 296555935@qq.com 445860279@qq.com -a /home/mysqlbackup/mysql$time.tar.gz</span><br />\r\n~<br />\r\n~</span></span></span>', 1380866457, 1380875151, 80, '未知', 50, 'linux脚本备份数据库 shell发送邮件', 1, 1, 1),
(11, '', '', 1, '', ' 步骤/方法 1 1.终端运行sudo apt-get remove wine，运行发现系统还有wine的图标残留，于是 2 2.删除~/.wine目录，这是隐藏文件夹，你要先在view下面，选show hidden files。 3 3.在~/.local/share/applications文件夹下删除wine目录和以wine-extension开头的desktop文件，把 mimeinfo.cache文件里和wine相关的内容去掉，把mimeapps.list里和wine相关的内容去掉 4 4.删除~/.local/share/mime/types，删除~/.local/share/mime/globs2，删除~/.local /', '<h2 class="exp-content-head">\r\n	步骤/方法\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 最简单是用 find / -name "*wine*"&nbsp; 查找出还有多少和wine有关的文件，手动删除或者用 find / -name "*wine*" -exec rm -fr {} \\;\r\n</p>\r\n<div class="exp-content-body">\r\n	<ol class="exp-conent-orderlist">\r\n		<li class="exp-content-list list-item-1">\r\n			<div class="list-icon">\r\n				1\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class="content-list-text">\r\n				1.终端运行sudo apt-get remove wine，运行发现系统还有wine的图标残留，于是<br />\r\n			</div>\r\n		</li>\r\n		<li class="exp-content-list list-item-2">\r\n			<div class="list-icon">\r\n				2\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class="content-list-text">\r\n				2.删除~/.wine目录，这是隐藏文件夹，你要先在view下面，选show hidden files。<br />\r\n			</div>\r\n		</li>\r\n		<li class="exp-content-list list-item-3">\r\n			<div class="list-icon">\r\n				3\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class="content-list-text">\r\n				3.在~/.local/share/applications文件夹下删除wine目录和以wine-extension开头的desktop文件，把\r\n mimeinfo.cache文件里和wine相关的内容去掉，把mimeapps.list里和wine相关的内容去掉<br />\r\n			</div>\r\n		</li>\r\n		<li class="exp-content-list list-item-4">\r\n			<div class="list-icon">\r\n				4\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class="content-list-text">\r\n				4.删除~/.local/share/mime/types，删除~/.local/share/mime/globs2，删除~/.local \r\n/share/mime/packages以x-wine- \r\nextension开头的所有文件。清空~/.local/share/mime/application里和wine相关的内容。<br />\r\n			</div>\r\n		</li>\r\n		<li class="exp-content-list list-item-5">\r\n			<div class="list-icon">\r\n				5\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class="content-list-text">\r\n				5.删除~/.config/menus/applications-merged目录<br />\r\n			</div>\r\n		</li>\r\n		<li class="exp-content-list list-item-6">\r\n			<div class="list-icon">\r\n				6\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class="content-list-text">\r\n				6.执行命令update-mime-database ~/.local/share/mime 更新文件类型数据库。\r\n			</div>\r\n		</li>\r\n	</ol>\r\n</div>', 1380943371, 1381036308, 69, '未知', 50, '卸载wine只需简单6个步骤', 1, 1, 1),
(12, '', '', 1, '', ' 在网站服务器上搭建好 Subversion 后，就可以通过 SVN 客户端来部署和管理程序代码了。每次对线上的程序代码进行修改时，都会产生一个新的版本号，并且随时可以回到以前的版本或下载以前版本的程序代码。此外，当多个人同时修改后，SVN 能够自动合并修改，并提示可能的冲突让你手动解决。 下面来介绍服务器上的安装步骤： svn的版本库用 svnadmin create 命令创建，可以配置svnserve.con', '<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	在\r\n网站服务器上搭建好 Subversion 后，就可以通过 SVN \r\n客户端来部署和管理程序代码了。每次对线上的程序代码进行修改时，都会产生一个新的版本号，并且随时可以回到以前的版本或下载以前版本的程序代码。此外，\r\n当多个人同时修改后，SVN 能够自动合并修改，并提示可能的冲突让你手动解决。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	下面来介绍服务器上的安装步骤：<br />\r\n<span><br />\r\nsvn的版本库用 svnadmin create 命令创建&nbsp;，可以配置svnserve.conf 设置多个版本库的配置文件</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	<span style="vertical-align:baseline;"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	<strong>1. 安装 Subversion</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	在 CentOS 上安装 Subversion 很容易，只要一条命令即可：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	<span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#C20CB9;font-weight:bold;">yum install</span> subversion\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	<br />\r\n在其他 Linux 发行版上，可以使用相应的包管理器来安装。例如 Ubuntu 上：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	<span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#C20CB9;font-weight:bold;">apt-get install</span> subversion\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	<strong>2. 建立 SVN 仓库</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	网站文件默认存放在 /home/admin/apacalzqz.tk&nbsp;目录。我们可以在 /home 目录下新建一个文件夹 repo，用来放置 SVN 仓库。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	<span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#C20CB9;font-weight:bold;">mkdir</span> <span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#660033;">-p</span> <span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#000000;font-weight:bold;">/</span>home<span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#000000;font-weight:bold;">/</span>repo<span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#000000;font-weight:bold;">/</span><br />\r\n<span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#C20CB9;font-weight:bold;">svnadmin</span> create <span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#000000;font-weight:bold;">/</span>home<span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#000000;font-weight:bold;">/</span>repo<span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#000000;font-weight:bold;">/apacalcms</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; // 这个是svn的版本库\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	SVN 仓库建立完成后，在目录下会生成一些配置文件。我们接着修改这些配置文件。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	<strong>3. 设置 SVN 账户及权限</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	首先修改 SVN 仓库的配置文件 /home/repo/wwwroot/conf/svnserve.conf 文件，修改以下项目：\r\n</p>\r\n[general]<br />\r\nanon-access = none<br />\r\nauth-access = write<br />\r\npassword-db = passwd<br />\r\nauthz-db = authz<br />\r\nrealm = wwwroot\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	然后建立账户，修改 /home/repo/wwwroot/conf/passwd 文件，添加账户和密码：\r\n</p>\r\n[general]<br />\r\n[users]<br />\r\nuser1 = password1<br />\r\nuser2 = password2<br />\r\nuser3 = password3<br />\r\nuser4 = password4<br />\r\nuser5 = password5\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	接下来是基于路径的访问控制，修改 /home/repo/wwwroot/conf/authz 文件，指定账户的权限：\r\n</p>\r\n[groups]<br />\r\ngroup1 = user1,user2<br />\r\n[/]              # 根目录权限设置<br />\r\nuser3 = rw       # user3权限是：读写<br />\r\nuser4 = r        # user4权限是：只读<br />\r\nuser5 =          # user5没有任何权限<br />\r\n@group1 = rw     # group1组权限是：读写\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	<strong>4. 设置自动更新网站程序目录</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	我\r\n们希望在通过 SVN 提交代码后，自动更新网站程序目录，方法是设置“钩子”。“钩子”是一段 Shell 脚本，在 SVN \r\n发生某个事件后自动被执行一次。通过设置 post-commit 钩子，可以让 SVN 在接到我们新提交的代码后，自动更新网站程序目录中的文件。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	添加 /home/repo/wwwroot/hooks/post-commit 文件：\r\n</p>\r\n<span style="vertical-align:baseline;font-style:italic;">#!/bin/sh<br />\r\nREPOS="$1"&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; # 版本库目录 /data2/svnrepos/rain<br />\r\nREV="$2"&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; # revision number<br />\r\n<br />\r\n# 若是apache提交的则不执行同步操作<br />\r\nAUTHOR=`/usr/bin/svnlook author -r $REV $REPOS`&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; # 执行提交的用户名<br />\r\nif [ "$AUTHOR" == "apache" ] ; <br />\r\nthen<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; exit;<br />\r\nfi<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTIME=`date ''+%F %T''`<br />\r\necho "[$TIME]--[$AUTHOR] svn commit file:" &gt;&gt; /home/logs/svnApacalcmsUpdate.log<br />\r\n<br />\r\n# 将修改了的文件同步更新到目标版本库<br />\r\nfor updatePath in `/usr/bin/svnlook changed -r $REV $REPOS | awk ''{print $2}''`<br />\r\ndo<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; fullUpdatePath="/home/apacle/public_html/$updatePath"<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; /usr/bin/svn update --username apacal --password ****** $fullUpdatePath &gt;&gt; /home/logs/svnApacalcmsUpdate.log<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; chmod g+w $fullUpdatePath<br />\r\ndone <br />\r\n</span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	别忘了设置为可执行：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	#<span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#C20CB9;font-weight:bold;">chmod</span> u+x <span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#000000;font-weight:bold;">/</span>home<span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#000000;font-weight:bold;">/</span>repo<span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#000000;font-weight:bold;">/</span>wwwroot<span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#000000;font-weight:bold;">/</span>hooks<span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#000000;font-weight:bold;">/</span>post-commit\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	<strong>5. 启动 svnserve</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	SVN 可以通过 Apache 等 Web 服务器来提供服务，也可以独立提供服务，两者各有优缺点，这里我们选择独立运行。启动 svnserve 后，就可以通过网络远程访问到 SVN 仓库了。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#C20CB9;font-weight:bold;">svnserve</span> <span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#660033;">-d</span> <span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#660033;">-r</span> <span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#000000;font-weight:bold;">/</span>home<span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#000000;font-weight:bold;">/</span>repo&nbsp;<span style="vertical-align:baseline;font-style:italic;"># 启动 &nbsp;这里为svn的根目录，如果想启动某个版本库，为 /home/repo/wwwroot<br />\r\n<span>&nbsp;</span></span><span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#C20CB9;font-weight:bold;">killall</span> <span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#C20CB9;font-weight:bold;">svnserve</span> <span style="vertical-align:baseline;font-style:italic;"># 停止</span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	另外，别忘了在防火墙上开放 svnserve 使用的端口，默认是 3690 端口。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	<strong>6. 签出到网站目录</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	SVN 仓库建立完成后，先初始签出到网站目录，以后就可以通过 svn update 来自动使网站目录中的文件和 SVN 仓库中的文件同步了。\r\n</p>\r\n<span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#C20CB9;font-weight:bold;">svn checkout</span> file:<span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#000000;font-weight:bold;">///</span>home<span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#000000;font-weight:bold;">/</span>repo<span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#000000;font-weight:bold;">/</span>wwwroot <span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#000000;font-weight:bold;">/</span>home<span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#000000;font-weight:bold;">/</span>wwwroot <span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#660033;">--username</span> user1 <span style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#660033;">--password</span> password1\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	<strong>7. 拒绝 Web 访问 .svn 目录</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	签出到网站目录后，网站目录下会生成一些 .svn 文件夹。这些文件夹中存放的是 SVN 系统使用的文件，我们不希望用户通过 Web 浏览到这些文件。通过修改服务器配置文件，我们可以做到：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	<em>Nginx：</em><br />\r\n在 nginx.conf 的 server 块中添加：\r\n</p>\r\nlocation ~ /\\. { access_log off; log_not_found off; deny all; }\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	<em>Apache：</em><br />\r\n在 httpd.conf 中添加：\r\n</p>\r\n<filesmatch "\\.svn="" .*"="">   Order Allow,Deny   Deny from all\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	重新载入服务器配置文件，让设置生效即可。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	<strong>8. 通过 SVN 客户端提交程序文件</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	使用刚才添加的账户和密码连接到 svn://【服务器地址】/ 就可以访问 SVN 仓库了。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	Windows 上最流行的 SVN 客户端是&nbsp;<a href="http://tortoisesvn.net/" target="_blank">TurtoiseSVN</a>。而对于 Mac 和 Linux，则通常使用 SVN 命令行客户端。关于这些客户端的使用方法，Sina App Engine 的文档中心有一个<a href="http://sae.sina.com.cn/?m=devcenter&catId=212" target="_blank">很不错的入门教程</a>可以参考。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	至此，我们完成了 SVN 服务的搭建。现在你可以通过 SVN 来更好地管理网站服务器上的程序文件了。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="vertical-align:baseline;color:#444444;font-family:''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', 1380945242, 1381036171, 109, '未知', 50, 'linux SVN 服务架设', 1, 1, 1);
